{"lemma":"رَيْبٌ","slug":"رَيْبٌ","root":"ر.#.ب","root_slug":"ر-_-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-_-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"رَيْب","root":"ريب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":18},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17216"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of رَابَ (rāba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"doubt, suspicion, uncertainty","examples":[{"text":"ذَٰلِكَ ٱلْكِتَـٰبُ لَا رَيْبَ فِيهِ هُدًى لِلْمُتَّقِينَ","english":"This is the Book about which there is no doubt, a guidance for those conscious of Allāh"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/rajb/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17216","headword_ar":"رَيْبٌ","root":"ryb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is an inf. n. of 1, (T, M, Mgh, Msb, &c.,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riybapN","text_ar":"رِيبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) or the latter is a simple subst.: (S, Msb:) the primary signification of the latter [and of the former also when it is used as a simple subst.] is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Disquiet, disturbance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agitation, of mind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh and Bd in ii. 1:) [and hence] the former signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doubt;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, Msb;) as also ↓ the latter; (S, Mgh;) because doubt disquiets, or disturbs, the mind: (Ksh and Bd ubi suprà, and Mgh:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"opinion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zan~N","text_ar":"ظَنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) and ↓ the latter, (S, M, A, Mgh, K,) and the former also, (M, A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doubt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspicion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil opinion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuhamapN","text_ar":"تُهَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Mgh, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zin~apN","text_ar":"ظِنَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, A, K:) or the former, [and ↓ the latter also,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doubt combined with suspicion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil opinion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an event,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a case, that occasions one doubt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspicion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil opinion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doubt combined with suspicion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil opinion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA raAbaka mino A^amorK","text_ar":"مَا رَابَكَ مِنْ اَمْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) [in this last sense, the latter is the more common: hence,] lying is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riybapN","text_ar":"رِيبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a trad. cited above: see 1: (Mgh:) the ↓ pl. of the latter is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyabN","text_ar":"رِيَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) A man, and a thing or an event or a case, is said to be ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw riybapK","text_ar":"ذُو رِيبَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having in him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, something occasioning doubt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspicion"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (A.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA rayoba","text_ar":"لَا رَيْبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"often occurs as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no doubt; without doubt; undoubtedly."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b2-  Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayobu Alz~amaAni","text_ar":"رَيْبُ الزَّمَانِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The accidents,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil accidents, of time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh and Bd ubi suprà, [in Fleischer's ed. of the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyab","text_ar":"رِيَب"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlzmAn","text_ar":"الزمان"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is more agreeable with the explanation, but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayob AlzmAn","text_ar":"رَيْب الزمان"},{"kind":"text","text":"is more usual,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that disquiet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disturb, the minds and hearts:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayobu Almanuwni","text_ar":"رَيْبُ المَنُونِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A) [which likewise signifies]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the accidents,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil accidents, of time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayobu Ald~ahori","text_ar":"رَيْبُ الدَّهْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same; i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sarofuhu","text_ar":"صَرْفُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Suruwfuhu","text_ar":"صُرُوفُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawaAdivuhu","text_ar":"حَوَادِثُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T. [This is said in the TA to be tropical; but I do not find"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1199},{"kind":"text","text":"it so characterized in the A.]) ―         -b3-  [Hence, likewise,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayobN","text_ar":"رَيْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A want; a needful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"requisite, thing, affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"business;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAjapN","text_ar":"حَاجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, A, Msb, K.) A poet says, (S,) namely, Kaab Ibn-Málik El-Ansáree, (TA,)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"qaDayonaA mino tihaAmapa kul~a rayobK\n                      \n                     \n                        wa xayobara vum~a A^ajoyayonaA Als~uyuwfaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We accomplished, from Tihámeh, every want, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Kheyber: then we gave rest to our swords"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.)       -A2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ryb","text_ar":"ريب"},{"kind":"text","text":"mentioned by Freytag as applied in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dls","text_ar":"دلس"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the S to a certain plant, and written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayob","text_ar":"رَيْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"in both of my copies of the S in that art., is a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabab","text_ar":"رَبَب"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the reading in the TA, pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rib~apN","text_ar":"رِبَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["M","K","S","Msb","A","Mgh","IAth","TA","Ksh","T"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}